           move      zero                 to   rr-nfa-max             .
           move      zero                 to   rr-nfi-min             .
           move      zero                 to   rr-nfi-max             .
           perform   vis-nfa-min-000      thru vis-nfa-min-999        .
           perform   vis-nfa-max-000      thru vis-nfa-max-999        .
       acc-tip-mov-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
